### Configuration

~~~ .php
File::$config = [
    // List of allowed file extension(s)
    'x' => [
        'gif' => 1,
        'html' => 1,
        'jpg' => 1,
        'json' => 1,
        'jpeg' => 1,
        'log' => 1,
        'png' => 1,
        'txt' => 1,
        'xml' => 1
    ],
    // Minimum and maximum file size allowed in byte(s)
    'size' => [0, 2097152]
];
~~~

Create a new file or open file if it already exists:

~~~ .php
$file = new File('.\path\to\file.txt');
~~~